Hey everyone :wave:!

My name’s Dani and I run the content marketing service <http://Scribly.io|Scribly.io>. We work with a range of clients across the world to deliver monthly content marketing plans. As an ex-freelance content marketer myself, the business is founded with a strong focus on creating a supportive space for our writers.

It can be so exploitative out there (I’ve experienced it myself), and so it’s really important to me that the guiding force of Scribly is to treat all of our writers fairly and as respected members of the team. I’m really happy to be part of this community :slightly_smiling_face:

If anyone is looking for freelance content marketing or copywriting opportunities, get in touch!

text: Hey <@U011UJX75PE>. It's a pretty wide range. It included web copy, email newsletters, social media, blog, some white paper work, and short video scripts for customer testimonials and product promos. For Rethink Robotics we focused on the manufacturing industry (robots working on the factory floor). And for RightHand Robotics, the products are piece-picking robots that automate part of the e-commerce fulfillment process in warehouses and distribution centers.
